title: Git1
content:
or create a new repository on the command line

echo "# jsondb" >> README.md
git init
git add README.md
git commit -m "first commit"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin https://github.com/2023emi/jsondb.git
git push -u origin main

title: Git2
content:

git branch -M main
git push -u origin main
